{"tid":1768630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：警方使用催淚彈前會顧及受影響人士","createTime":"2019-12-04T08:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T10:13:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4fd08e6885631d053d47d59fef616bedacf7ec8e","tid":1768630,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"有議員不滿警方多次在安老院舍外施放催淚彈，擔心影響體弱人士。政府回應議員質詢指，無收過報告有院舍受催淚彈嚴重影響，強調警方施放催淚彈前會顧及受影響人士。<br />\n<br />\n持續近半年的示威，警方施放約一萬枚催淚彈，曾經多次在安老院舍外施放。<br />\n<br />\n有議員關注催淚彈對福利服務單位的影響。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光指警方在行動前亦會呼籲附近院舍留意，有議員不滿通告內容過分簡單；建制派則針對示威者的暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n兼任行會成員的劉業強要求公開催淚彈成分，羅致光指因應警方行動，不能公開催淚彈成分。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PDLnWFsyWPIq1eeiMg0QUg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/L-TEARGAS-191204-14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPDLnWFsyWPIq1eeiMg0QUg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FL-TEARGAS-191204-14.jpg&h=92c81ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%83%E9%A1%A7%E5%8F%8A%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-062711833.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB-062711833.html&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=f6e7a4ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88